//  GitHub Actions Cheatsheet
//!  ⏰ UTC → PHT Conversion Table
//  | UTC Time | PHT Time         | Notes    |
//  | -------- | ---------------- | -------- |
//  | 00:00    | 08:00            | Morning  |
//  | 01:00    | 09:00            |          |
//  | 02:00    | 10:00            |          |
//  | 03:00    | 11:00            |          |
//  | 04:00    | 12:00            | Noon     |
//  | 05:00    | 13:00            |          |
//  | 06:00    | 14:00            |          |
//  | 07:00    | 15:00            |          |
//  | 08:00    | 16:00            |          |
//  | 09:00    | 17:00            |          |
//  | 10:00    | 18:00            |          |
//  | 11:00    | 19:00            |          |
//  | 12:00    | 20:00            | Evening  |
//  | 13:00    | 21:00            |          |
//  | 14:00    | 22:00            |          |
//  | 15:00    | 23:00            |          |
//  | 16:00    | 00:00 (next day) | Midnight |
//  | 17:00    | 01:00 (next day) |          |
//  | 18:00    | 02:00 (next day) |          |
//  | 19:00    | 03:00 (next day) |          |
//  | 20:00    | 04:00 (next day) |          |
//  | 21:00    | 05:00 (next day) |          |
//  | 22:00    | 06:00 (next day) |          |
//  | 23:00    | 07:00 (next day) |          |
// 

